room_title: Escape room "The Study" by The Locked Inn in Grover Beach
room_address: 750 Farroll Road​ Suite C, ​Grover Beach, CA 93433
room_description:
Located on our 3rd floor, The Study will introduce a new level of adventure to The Locked Inn.  The Study allows guests to masquerade as a well known professor of archaeology and delve into his potential ties with a secret society.  This room is filled to the brim with adventure and secrets.
Will you be able to retrieve his lost artifact, or will you be forgotten and lost in the mists of time?  Book your adventure today!
